{"tid":1506202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《人民日報》深夜發微博稱踐踏國旗挑戰權威涉觸犯法例","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T18:12:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4774958e69861583f86106b6f0d0178d932d250a","tid":1506202,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"本港政府發言人表示，昨日有示威者在葵涌運動場，取下國旗，並肆意踐踏，行為挑戰國家權威，亦涉嫌觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》。<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》在微博發表評論，形容鮮豔的五星紅旗，孤獨躺在地上，遭示威者踐踏，是讓人痛心和憤怒。評論說，如此挑釁是羞辱國家尊嚴，傷害十四億國人的情感，形容是毫無敬畏，變本加厲，「是該付出代價了」。<br />\n<br />\n評論又表示，要警告暴徒，侮辱國旗不只是犯法，更涉嫌犯罪，必將受到法律嚴懲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476772-20190826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476772-20190826.htm&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=1374c200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476772-20190826.htm&h=4220ffbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476772-20190826.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2cfaa85227839541c38cd34099723df8153f600e","tid":1506202,"uid":5793,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"跪求出老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d87d5ae18150bbac82cf4a6204e50697ae5aca","tid":1506202,"uid":58852,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"亮劍美帝未???"},{"pid":"751e68dc66748bd7981ddec28d9e67f77951aeb9","tid":1506202,"uid":282435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"嚴正口交"},{"pid":"83a5f0f4385fd823536d149c51637a4429b35906","tid":1506202,"uid":264868,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qmoo9u2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQmoo9u2.jpg&h=d6b5cefc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講緊佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec01cdb3b888778c5482bc7de51dd1f54b411e03","tid":1506202,"uid":275370,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyWNRJD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyWNRJD.png&h=c0d33966&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a5e7e345a7d101b113657c0c7fb46f7ebf3ccf5","tid":1506202,"uid":259015,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"敵人反對的<br />\n即是做對了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>勇武巴打ho ball<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f7ed34574c0c90ca4ccf4605c3bd54074855a157","tid":1506202,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/37a0c1af0cd95b5ca0df41271f859f95/tumblr_inline_ny5ykgMVBP1ta1qoy_500.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F37a0c1af0cd95b5ca0df41271f859f95%2Ftumblr_inline_ny5ykgMVBP1ta1qoy_500.png&h=b670537f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b76dcb597075ebfc23bf58880a8c2bbf1a8a84f","tid":1506202,"uid":12412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7KEGIyKlDzs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7KEGIyKlDzs&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=c681c4e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7KEGIyKlDzs</a><br />\n踩住國旗執錢好暴力呀"},{"pid":"392b9bdc5ec6ccbd0e9220591943436b746a46bc","tid":1506202,"uid":36148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:07:49.000Z","msg":"放過國旗先，踩黨旗"},{"pid":"5156bc4da8c79b72da81b7a39be08e9750ffcece","tid":1506202,"uid":279326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-free-6090078-1.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbbs.tianya.cn%2Fm%2Fpost-free-6090078-1.shtml&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=6b1648ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bbs.tianya.cn/m/post-free-6090078-1.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n以前流行一句說話<br />\n<br />\n南高登 北天涯<br />\n<br />\n天涯討論區算是在極權之下<br />\n<br />\n稍為有開放思想的中國討論區<br />\n<br />\n其中有網民說<br />\n<br />\n【呵呵，谁敢说现在的香港不会成为秦朝的大泽乡？】<br />\n<br />\n反秦起義就是大澤鄉 陳勝吳廣起義<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n網民Ａ<br />\n<br />\n工作一辈子，都买不起房子，看不到想希望，你觉得，要咋整？<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｂ<br />\n<br />\n从娃娃抓起，爱国？无私奉献？抬高房价？年轻人生存都成了问题，还教育什么？<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｃ<br />\n<br />\n社会制度不同，就像水和火一样不可调和。除非水变火，火变水。<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｄ<br />\n<br />\n说好了是50年不变，为什么20多年就想变、就想改、就像当家做主，这也太急了。<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｅ<br />\n<br />\n你要爬在地上，什么 ，还想站着，你的思想觉悟呢，你的家国情怀呢<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｆ<br />\n<br />\n非慕洋犬们为什么会在瑞士银行有7.8万亿，这也是匪夷所思的事情<br />\n<br />\n網民Ｇ<br />\n<br />\n现在网络这么发达，监控头这么多，为什么电视报道、现场直播等视频都没有？到底是怎样的暴徒，能否像报道法国黄背心一样报道<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄 香港人要加油<br />\n<br />\n牆內很多人也默默支持香港示威者"},{"pid":"0a8673cd381b3a4032a12f5ce98a6c69a353096b","tid":1506202,"uid":27167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cfaa85227839541c38cd34099723df8153f600e","tid":1506202,"uid":5793,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"跪求出老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"9702f1955d756ee352e2600ee3dc51744b1a436f","tid":1506202,"uid":247845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"所以要出老解未?"},{"pid":"d0a4eed7c427e2f0e4dfe3e84689dd03e47f63a8","tid":1506202,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl